high_descs: Turn left walk forward then head to the left cabinet above the microwave
Open the cabinet and pick up the mug then close the cabinet
Turn right then walk forward head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the mug then close the fridge
Turn left and head to the cabinet beside the fridge
Open the cabinet put in the mug then close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled mug in the cabinet

high_descs: Walk to the left, turn left near the cabinet, walk straight a little bit, turn right to go to the microwave and look up to the cabinet on top of it.
Open the cabinet, pick up a cup that is in the cabinet and close the cabinet.
Turn around, walk slightly to the front and turn left to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the cup on the rack next to the black plate, close the fridge, let it cool for a while, pick it up again and close the fridge.
Go slightly to the left to the cabinet beside the fridge.
Open the cabinet under the counter top, put the cup in it and close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Store a cold cup in the cabinet under the counter top beside the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the microwave and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the left cabinet in front of you and take out the white mug, then close the cabinet.
Turn around and walk over to the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge, after a couple seconds take out the mug and close the fridge.
Walk over to the section of counter that is to the left of the fridge.
Open the cabinet door below the counter and put the chilled mug inside, then close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled white mug in a cabinet.
